    self.invalidate_cached_bitmap();
}
```

This calls `self.invalidate_cached_bitmap()` on the Graphic. The `invalidate_cached_bitmap()` is the public function that walks up parents:

```rust
fn invalidate_cached_bitmap(self) {
    if self.base().invalidate_cached_bitmap() {
