8. animated MovieClip calls `run_frame_internal` which queues PlaceObject tags
9. animated MovieClip dequeues PlaceObject tags and processes them
10. `Replace` action calls `child.replace_with(context, id)` on the Graphic → `invalidate_cached_bitmap`

Step 7 is a no-op for Graphic - no `invalidate_cached_bitmap` is called. So when step 10 calls `invalidate_cached_bitmap`, the flag should NOT be set yet. The chain should walk up properly.

